<div class="title">Bitter 'Blue' Wine</div>
<div class="substance">Nymphaea nouchali var caerulea & Alcohol - Wine</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=splice&Exact=1">splice</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; splice. "Bitter 'Blue' Wine: An Experience with Nymphaea nouchali var caerulea & Alcohol - Wine (exp46557)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Apr 24, 2007. erowid.org/exp/46557</div>

<br/>



